title: Very heavy rain alert for TN, AP as Ditwah readies to sail past Sri Lanka - PressReader
article_text: WASHINGTON — Pres­id­ent Trump said Thursday that one of the two National Guard mem­bers allegedly shot by an Afghan national near the White House a day earlier had died, call­ing the sus­pect — who had worked with the CIA in his nat­ive coun­try — a “sav­age mon­ster.”
